  "name": "Empty Hardware Services remover Automation Script",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"empty-hardware-services-remover-automation-script\">Empty Hardware Services remover Automation Script</h1>\n<p><strong>This Automation script is to remove all the Empty, non-used Hardware services, that are not assigned to a register, within the Hardware Services.</strong></p>\n<p>The reason for the script is to clean all empty entries, making the hardware service menu easier to located computers/hardware-services/IP-addresses, during troubleshooting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png\" alt=\"mceclip2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069476983567/mceclip2.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<hr></hr><h2 id=\"Installation\" data-id=\"installation\">Installation</h2>\n<p>Before beginning, you will be required to install an open-source Browser Extension from<span> </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fui.vision%2F\">UI Vision</a> (unless already installed you may skip this step)</p>\n<p>From there once the installation is complete, you may import the Scripts into the extension and continue to the Database with the error entries to remove.</p>\n<hr></hr><h2 id=\"Running_the_Script\" data-id=\"running-the-script\">Running the Script</h2>\n<ol><li>Download<span> </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fui.vision%2F\">Ui Vision</a><span> </span>- <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fui.vision%2F\">https://ui.vision/</a> (<strong>unless already installed you may skip this step</strong>)</li><li>Download the Zip file containing a JSON file named:\n<ol><li>Empty Hardware Service remover</li></ol></li><li>Import the file using the import-file/zip<br/><br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png\" alt=\"mceclip1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056807326223/mceclip1.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li><li>Open a NEW Browser window</li><li>Log into the Database</li><li>Open UI Vision in your Extension list<br/><br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png\" alt=\"mceclip2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056810467727/mceclip2.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><br/></li><li>Go to<strong> Settings &gt; POS Settings &gt; Hardware Services</strong> in the Database</li><li>Select the script - Empty Hardware Service Remover</li><li>Play the Script in a loop with UI Vision<br/><br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png\" alt=\"mceclip4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056870013583/mceclip4.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png\" alt=\"mceclip6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5056877027471/mceclip6.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><br/></li><li>Once complete you may stop the Loop<br/><br/><img src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png\" alt=\"mceclip0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/5069419253775/mceclip0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/></li></ol><p> </p>",
